The Journal has published several articles critical of the World Bank and the 
International Monetary Fund. These articles have shown the damage caused by the 
neoliberal policies advocated by these agencies to the health and quality of 
life of the people in countries where such policies are carried out. Published 
here are excerpts of a speech given by Joseph Stiglitz, senior economist of the 
